{"tid":759920,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"《魔獸世界》聯盟香港本土公會 Essence 招人","createTime":"2018-07-29T05:49:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-07T04:02:29.000Z","uid":172454,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"61490922ba166a3c08b47c357b2902ea48b4d725","tid":759920,"uid":172454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T05:49:26.000Z","msg":"為迎接魔獸世界新版本《決戰艾澤拉斯》即將於 8 月 14 日上市，希望籍此招募所有有興趣既新手或老手一齊玩。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://bnetcmsus-a.akamaihd.net/cms/gallery/4AZA9DK8WTBS1517347770194.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbnetcmsus-a.akamaihd.net%2Fcms%2Fgallery%2F4AZA9DK8WTBS1517347770194.jpg&h=db82eedc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://wow.zamimg.com/uploads/screenshots/normal/698470.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwow.zamimg.com%2Fuploads%2Fscreenshots%2Fnormal%2F698470.jpg&h=f98084e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jSJr3dXZfcg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjSJr3dXZfcg&d=l529D9%2FMuNwcFbTqbOpFY26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=ad8ad0a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jSJr3dXZfcg</a><br />\n<br />\n伺服器：台服　暗影之月／眾星之子／語風<br />\n陣營　：聯盟<br />\n公會　：Essence<br />\n公會簡介：本公會原身為水晶之刺部落老牌香港公會，曾為台服最大香港公會之一。<br />\n經歷浩劫與重生、潘達利亞之謎、德拉諾之霸、軍臨天下版本，現在最新版本決戰艾澤拉斯創立暗影之月聯盟分會，希望匯聚香港聯盟玩家一同享受遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n公會方向：暫會以半休閒公會形式運行，初期目標建立一團１０－２０人副本固定團，並定期舉辦公會休閒副本活動。<br />\n公會FB：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/WoWHKEssence/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FWoWHKEssence%2F&d=l529D9%2FMuNwcFbTqbOpFY26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=96277d94\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/WoWHKEssence/</a><br />\n公會Youtube：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/HKEssence\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fuser%2FHKEssence&d=l529D9%2FMuNwcFbTqbOpFY26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=b0ed6fb7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/user/HKEssence</a><br />\n<br />\n固定團詳情：<br />\n日子：待定（一星期２&mdash;３日）<br />\n時間：晚上９&mdash;１２<br />\n空缺：任何<br />\n<br />\n有興趣既朋友可以ADD：<br />\nBNET：syicheung#4357<br />\nTelegram：HKEssence (<a href=\"https://t.me/HKEssence\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKEssence&d=l529D9%2FMuNwcFbTqbOpFY26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=20f5f749\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKEssence</a>)<br />\n<br />\n無論你係PVE/PVP向，新手/老手，專業/休閒玩家，只要你有興趣玩，只要你係香港人，快Ｄ加入啦！"},{"pid":"62dc68e634deb8f285add717bb9bc5e0c7e008c7","tid":759920,"uid":101688,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T06:04:02.000Z","msg":"日落lm路過"},{"pid":"c1e7985b980c8a15887dfed1c01749d5c631dc4e","tid":759920,"uid":172454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T07:09:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac981bcae2c39a820b72c1bcaa60b18ef1ea02ec","tid":759920,"uid":172454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T08:01:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"291ffc980c2fbd32e7f7b9585b9dd31eba9142c1","tid":759920,"uid":172454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T08:26:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c09aea1f73fb67f013347426d82c73f964ffdcb","tid":759920,"uid":172454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T10:15:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e21d246ff1e74b95d6af863a142d3fa0c32aef13","tid":759920,"uid":187108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T10:25:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"59752f96fc3fd01cc2e7296ee06163397e171faa","tid":759920,"uid":84514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T10:27:27.000Z","msg":"For the Horde!"},{"pid":"ac5fc9d3d9d8eefbd2f47fa630af4c6f0a1b63ed","tid"